ing: 1 (4 ounce) can diced green chiles, drained
des: "This is a cool, refreshing dip that can be served anytime. Serve with chips, crackers or sliced vegetables.  Exceptional with Hawaiian bread."
ins: In a medium-size mixing bowl, combine Mexican-style corn, green chilis, green onions, sour cream, jalapeno pepper, mayonnaise, and cheddar cheese. Mix well. Cover and refrigerate until ready to serve.
